Personally, I&#39;d convert the `String` values to `int` (inches) up-front, this gives you the opportunity to deal with possible errors during conversation.

    ArrayList&lt;String&gt; heights = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();
    heights.add(&quot;5&#39;11&quot;);
